data.description:
Welcome to your new three-bedroom, one bathroom home on a dead-end street, offering the perfect blend of comfort, privacy, and timeless appeal. The heart of this home lies in its open concept living areas, seamlessly connecting the kitchen, dining, and living room. Whether you're entertaining guests or enjoying a quiet evening with family, this layout fosters togetherness and creates a welcoming atmosphere. Each room is thoughtfully designed to offer comfort and functionality, ensuring everyone has their own space to relax and unwind.
This home has a modern electric fireplace in the living area, beautifully painted cabinets in the kitchen and granite counter tops. It has so much room for kids to play, pets to enjoy, or for you to have a large garden with abundant space remaining. There is also a two-car open-ended garage for covered parking needs. Beat the summer heat and create lasting memories with family and friends in your very own above-ground pool. Perfect for refreshing dips on hot days and leisurely lounging in the sun, the pool adds a touch of luxury and fun to your backyard retreat.
